### =============================================================
### AlAshmar API - Semester Reports Controller
### Base URL: http://localhost:5107
### =============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5107
@authToken  = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@semesterId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003

# =============================================================
# SemesterReportsController  - Semester-Level Reports
# =============================================================

### Get semester overview report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/semesters/{{semesterId}}/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get semester statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/semesters/{{semesterId}}/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get top students in semester (default top count)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/semesters/{{semesterId}}/top-students
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get top students in semester (custom top count)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/semesters/{{semesterId}}/top-students?top=5
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get top teachers in semester (default top count)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/semesters/{{semesterId}}/top-teachers
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get top teachers in semester (custom top count)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/semesters/{{semesterId}}/top-teachers?top=5
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get class summaries in semester
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/semesters/{{semesterId}}/classes
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###
